{"tid":1503980,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"在中國受訓及新聞系畢業的女記者到澳洲後變節，接受澳洲傳媒專訪踢爆中共宣傳機器如何運作","createTime":"2019-08-25T06:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T07:06:02.000Z","uid":134993,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"44dee4ba5596d9296cbadeb0f1c4d4c2ab217527","tid":1503980,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:56:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Y-jLyjMux2c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FY-jLyjMux2c&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=6d167ae5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Y-jLyjMux2c</a>"},{"pid":"bb63ab3407b0d6c91eaeec42767c536c304e096f","tid":1503980,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2ec0b925972ac2b39d29154b39e1967060e24d","tid":1503980,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:00:29.000Z","msg":"應該要睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0141b3ba162bd1cc940d8d5b3caa41044c8de7e7","tid":1503980,"uid":72800,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:13:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">破而後立</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nFfam93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnFfam93.jpg&h=f46c0dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n'If not us, <strong>WHO</strong>? <br />\nIf not now, <strong>WHEN</strong>?'<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">RIGHT THE WRONG, FREE HONG KONG</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><em>毋忘六烈 八百義 兩眼 三十骨折 手腳筋<br />\n過期毒氣 元朗黑夜 811警暴 雙肺 一裙 無數屈辱私刑<br />\n撤回 定性 釋士 究警 普選</em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n試問誰還未發聲<br />\n都捨我其誰<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>衛我城</strong></span><br />\n天生有權還有心可作主<br />\n誰要認命噤聲</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qmfE8Gr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqmfE8Gr.jpg&h=24d31a61&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Be Water</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Push HARDER than yesterday<br />\nIf you want a DIFFERENT TOMORROW</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">中國威脅論\n打壓外資 染紅企業\n清算航運龍頭大本營\n白色恐怖橫行\n貨幣操控 嚴重影響全球經濟\n反人道 暴力主義\n反人權 軍事鎮壓\n誣陷扣留外國領事館職員\n公然宣佈國際聲明已成歷史\n人面識別系統全面入侵私隱\n智能燈柱RFID監察行動痕跡 WiFi隱患\n信用系統標籤分等 限制人身權利打壓異己\n施壓公共交通系統公司\n施壓司法機關系統\n掌控執法部門成管治機器\n新聞媒體自由封鎖 假新聞一言定音\n不容異見之聲 網絡圍牆封鎖屏蔽 \n宣揚一人執政黨國 造王英雄主義\n改造信仰 壓抑宗教自由\n中國人納粹主義浪潮入侵西方主義國家\n新疆教育營文化滅絕非我族類\n六四屠殺事件 歷史檔案依然封鎖\n維權人士牢獄之災 每年逃亡海外\n陳秋實律師片段、多位內地藝術家遭禁聲\n強制拘留 驗血 政治檢控 勞改\n人民日報種族歧視深膚色人種\n警隊內部以&lsquo;甲甴&rsquo;爭議詞代指運動人士\n過期催淚彈CS神經毒氣 大量存放使用 社區災難\n解僱 清算 追捕 人面拍攝 ID追蹤</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><div style=\"text-align: right;\">&lsquo;&lsquo;We work in the dark to serve the light.&rsquo;&rsquo;</div></span>"},{"pid":"a998a350bf673ce9767e355a27f4e18b9c1a53c0","tid":1503980,"uid":296835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:16:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"31a2f76304e0882cc0bdcc22732f327fd16f99b0","tid":1503980,"uid":134381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:52:10.000Z","msg":"有冇原片?"},{"pid":"360a217e3bbf0e170b29722cb033e50c6322f1b5","tid":1503980,"uid":135542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:00:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"